* Protect s3 bucket

Replicate it in another region under another account with different IAM accounts. The source cannot control it anymore.

- [[https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/whats-new/2017/11/amazon-s3-adds-new-features-for-data-security-and-compliance/]]
